node.text:
JOIN ME TODAY at @turningpointusa in Tampa, Florida!

I will be hosting a show from 1-2 pm ET on @foxnation and then speaking LIVE at 4:30 pm ET!

Watching free at foxnation.com with code SAS!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KayleighMcEnany on July 16, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, palm trees and text that says 'A CTPUSA SAS ALL ACCESS LIVE! FOX NATION Sunday, July 18 Tuesday, July 20'.

node.text:
I am PUMPED to host LIVE shows from @turningpointusa in Tampa with Pete Hegseth on @foxnation !

You can watch my speech at #SAS2021 & our show Sun/Mon/Tues. Speech is 4:30 & first show is at 1:00 on Sunday!

It's free to sign up for Fox Nation using code SAS at foxnation.com!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KayleighMcEnany on July 10, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and baby.
